09:39.046 --> 09:41.680
We need to make sure
the activity in the main home

09:41.682 --> 09:44.616
is safe for both
Michelle and her guests.

09:44.618 --> 09:48.119
Tonight we will focus
on the Lady in White, Jacob,

09:48.121 --> 09:50.221
